Description: Sparebanken Ost is a Norway-based savings bank. The Bank is engaged in the provision of both banking and financial products and services to individuals and businesses. It offers products and services to business customers in the central Eastern Norway region. The primary market area is the lower part of Buskerud County and the Drammen region. Its product and service offering includes loans, mortgage loan, cards, savings accounts, payment services, pension funds, life and non-life insurance, investment services and online banking services. The Banks three core products are savings products, credit products and payment products. In addition, it distributes insurance, fund shares, interest rate hedging, and currency. Sparebanken Ost Boligkreditt AS, AS Financiering, Sparebanken Ost Eiendom AS, Ost Prosjekt AS and Ost Inkasso AS are among Bank's subsidiaries.
